Evaluations.Expression: smCountThisSignal = true
smThisIsALocus = 1

smChannelHasExcessiveNoise = smTestForExcessiveNoisePreset AND ((smChannelHasExcessiveNoiseAboveAnalysisThreshold AND smTestExcessiveNoiseAboveOrBelowAnalysisThreshold) OR (smChannelHasExcessiveNoiseAboveDetectionThreshold AND NOT smTestExcessiveNoiseAboveOrBelowAnalysisThreshold))
smIsSample = NOT smSampleIsLadder
smIsSampleButNotNegativeCtrl = smIsSample AND NOT smSampleIsNegCtrl
smDisableFractionalFilter = smDisableLowLevelFiltersForKnownMixturesPreset AND smSampleSatisfiesPossibleMixtureIDCriteria AND smDisableFractionalFilterPreset
smDisablePullupFractionalFilter = smDisableLowLevelFiltersForKnownMixturesPreset AND smSampleSatisfiesPossibleMixtureIDCriteria AND smDisablePullupFractionalFilterPreset
smDisableStutterFilter = smDisableLowLevelFiltersForKnownMixturesPreset AND smSampleSatisfiesPossibleMixtureIDCriteria AND smDisableStutterFilterPreset
smDisableAdenylationFilter = smDisableLowLevelFiltersForKnownMixturesPreset AND smSampleSatisfiesPossibleMixtureIDCriteria AND smDisableAdenylationFilterPreset
smInferredFFLeft = smPartOfExtendedLocusLeft AND smHeightBelowFractionalFilter AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter
smInferredFFRight = smPartOfExtendedLocusRight AND smHeightBelowFractionalFilter AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter
smInferredPullupFFLeft = smPartOfExtendedLocusLeft AND smHeightBelowPullupFractionalFilter AND NOT smDisablePullupFractionalFilter
smInferredPullupFFRight = smPartOfExtendedLocusRight AND smHeightBelowPullupFractionalFilter AND NOT smDisablePullupFractionalFilter

smFFLeft = ((smBelowFractionalFilterLeft AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter) OR (smBelowPullupFractionalFilterLeft AND NOT smDisablePullupFractionalFilter) OR smInferredFFLeft OR smInferredPullupFFLeft)

smFFRight = ((smBelowFractionalFilterRight AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter) OR (smBelowPullupFractionalFilterRight AND NOT smDisablePullupFractionalFilter) OR smInferredFFRight OR smInferredPullupFFRight)

smExtendedFractionalFilter = ((NOT smPartOfExtendedLocusRight AND smFFLeft) OR (NOT smPartOfExtendedLocusLeft AND smFFRight) OR (smFFLeft AND smFFRight)) AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter AND NOT smPeakInCoreLadderLocus

smUnassignedInterlocusPeak = NOT (smPeakInCoreLadderLocus OR smPartOfExtendedLocusLeft OR smPartOfExtendedLocusRight OR smSampleIsLadder OR smSignalIsCtrlPeak OR smUnexpectedILSPeak OR smChannelIsILS)
smUnexpectedPeakInNegativeControl = smSampleIsNegCtrl AND NOT smChannelIsILS AND NOT smIsQualityLocus
smPurePullup = smPullUp AND NOT smPrimaryInterchannelLink AND NOT smNotInterchannelLink
smTemp1Left = sm0UnambiguousPeaksLeft AND NOT sm0UnambiguousPeaksRight
smTemp1Right = sm0UnambiguousPeaksRight AND NOT sm0UnambiguousPeaksLeft
smTemp2Left = (smAcceptedOLLeft AND NOT smAcceptedOLRight) AND NOT smTemp1Right
smTemp2Right = (smAcceptedOLRight AND NOT smAcceptedOLLeft) AND NOT smTemp1Left
smTemp3Left = (smFFRight AND NOT smFFLeft) AND NOT (smTemp1Right OR smTemp2Right)
smTemp3Right = (smFFLeft AND NOT smFFRight) AND NOT (smTemp1Left OR smTemp2Left)
smTemp5Left = (smExcessiveResidualDisplacementRight AND NOT smExcessiveResidualDisplacementLeft) AND NOT (smTemp1Right OR smTemp2Right OR smTemp3Right)
smTemp5Right = (smExcessiveResidualDisplacementLeft AND NOT smExcessiveResidualDisplacementRight) AND NOT (smTemp1Left OR smTemp2Left OR smTemp3Left)
smTemp6Left = (sm1UnambiguousPeakLeft AND sm2PlusUnambiguousPeaksRight) AND NOT (smTemp1Right OR smTemp2Right OR smTemp3Right OR smTemp5Right)
smTemp6Right = (sm1UnambiguousPeakRight AND sm2PlusUnambiguousPeaksLeft) AND NOT (smTemp1Left OR smTemp2Left OR smTemp3Left OR smTemp5Left)
smTemp7Left = smTemp1Left OR ((smTemp2Left OR smTemp3Left OR smTemp5Left OR smTemp6Left OR smSignalIsIntegralMultipleOfRepeatLeft) AND NOT smFFLeft)
smTemp7Right = smTemp1Right OR ((smTemp2Right OR smTemp3Right OR smTemp5Right OR smTemp6Right OR smSignalIsIntegralMultipleOfRepeatRight) AND NOT smFFRight)
smCouldBelongToLocusLeft = (smTemp7Left AND smPartOfExtendedLocusLeft) AND NOT smTemp7Right AND NOT (smPeakInCoreLadderLocus AND NOT smSignalOL)
smCouldBelongToLocusRight = (smTemp7Right AND smPartOfExtendedLocusRight) AND NOT smTemp7Left AND NOT (smPeakInCoreLadderLocus AND NOT smSignalOL)
smPullUpAtControlPeak = smSignalIsCtrlPeak AND smPullUp

smInterlocusPullUp = (NOT (smPeakInCoreLadderLocus OR smSampleIsLadder OR smPartOfExtendedLocusLeft OR smPartOfExtendedLocusRight OR smSignalIsCtrlPeak OR smChannelIsILS)) AND (smPullUp OR smCalculatedPurePullup)
smInterlocusPullUpWithPoorFit = smInterlocusPullUp AND (smPoorPeakMorphology OR smCurveFitMarginal OR smCurveFitFailed)
smPullupAtExtraneousILSPeak = smChannelIsILS AND smPullUp AND smUnexpectedILSPeak
smPossibleValidInterlocusLeft = smCouldBelongToLocusLeft
smPossibleValidInterlocusRight = smPartOfExtendedLocusRight AND NOT (smFFRight OR smInterlocusPullUp)
smValidOLInterlocusLeft = smCouldBelongToLocusLeft
smValidOLInterlocusRight = smCouldBelongToLocusRight
smAcceptedInterlocusLeft = smPossibleValidInterlocusLeft AND smAcceptedOLLeft
smAcceptedInterlocusRight = smPossibleValidInterlocusRight AND smAcceptedOLRight
smLaserOffScaleForTrigger = smLaserOffScale
smDoNotCall = (smAdenylation AND (NOT smCallOnLadderAdenylationPreset OR smSignalOL))

Triggers.TriggerExpression: smStutter (NOT smBelowMinRFU AND NOT smDisableStutterFilter): smNumberOfStuttersInSample

Evaluations.Expression: smRestrictedPriorityPeak = (smHeightBelowInterlocusMinRFU OR smBelowMinRFU OR smRedundantPeak OR (smHeightBelowFractionalFilter AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter) OR (smHeightBelowPullupFractionalFilter AND NOT smDisablePullupFractionalFilter) OR smInterlocusPullUp OR (smExtendedFractionalFilter AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter AND NOT (smPeakInCoreLadderLocus AND NOT smSignalOL)) OR smPullupAtExtraneousILSPeak OR smLadderPeakOutsideCoreLadder) AND NOT ((smSampleIsNegCtrl AND NOT smChannelIsILS) OR smSignalIsCtrlPeak)
smNonEditableRestrictedPriorityPeak = (smRestrictedPriorityPeak AND NOT smBelowMinRFU) AND NOT smAllowEditingRestrictedPriorityPreset
smEditableRestrictedPriorityPeak = (smRestrictedPriorityPeak AND NOT smBelowMinRFU) AND smAllowEditingRestrictedPriorityPreset
smBelowMinRFURestrictedPriorityPeak = (smRestrictedPriorityPeak AND smBelowMinRFU) AND NOT (smAllowEditingRestrictedPriorityPreset AND smAllowEditingPeaksBelowMinRFUPreset)
smEditableBelowMinRFURestrictedPriorityPeak = (smRestrictedPriorityPeak AND smBelowMinRFU) AND (smAllowEditingRestrictedPriorityPreset AND smAllowEditingPeaksBelowMinRFUPreset)
smTrueCrater = smCrater AND NOT smSignalNotACrater
smTrueCraterSidePeak = smCraterSidePeak AND NOT smSignalNotACraterSidePeak
smPullUpAtAllele = smSignalIsAllele AND smPullUp AND NOT smRestrictedPriorityPeak
smAlleleOL = smSignalOL AND smSignalIsAllele AND NOT (smRestrictedPriorityPeak OR smSampleIsPosCtrl)
smActuallyAnAllele = smSignalIsAllele AND NOT smRestrictedPriorityPeak AND NOT smSampleIsLadder AND NOT smChannelIsILS AND NOT smUnassignedInterlocusPeak
smCoreAlleleIsOL = smActuallyAnAllele AND smAlleleOL AND smPeakInCoreLadderLocus
smPurePullupLateStage = smPurePullup OR smCalculatedPurePullup OR smPartialPullupBelowMinRFU

smNotAKnownArtifact = NOT ((smStutter AND NOT smDisableStutterFilter) OR (smAdenylation AND NOT smDisableAdenylationFilter AND NOT (smCallOnLadderAdenylationPreset AND NOT smSignalOL)) OR (smPullUp AND NOT smNotInterchannelLink) OR smCalculatedPurePullup OR smSpike OR (((smHeightBelowFractionalFilter OR smExtendedFractionalFilter)) AND NOT smDisableFractionalFilter AND smIncludeFractionalFilterAmongKnownArtifactsToEvaluateSubAnalyticPeaksPreset))

smAmbiguousInterlocus = NOT (smCouldBelongToLocusLeft AND smCouldBelongToLocusRight) AND NOT smChannelIsILS AND NOT smSampleIsLadder AND NOT (smPeakInCoreLadderLocus AND NOT smSignalOL) AND (smPartOfExtendedLocusLeft AND smPartOfExtendedLocusRight) AND NOT smPossibleAmbiguousInterlocusAssignedToLocus
smAmbiguousCoreVsExtendedLeft = NOT smChannelIsILS AND NOT smSampleIsLadder AND (smPeakInCoreLadderLocus AND smSignalOL) AND smPartOfExtendedLocusLeft
smAmbiguousCoreVsExtendedRight = NOT smChannelIsILS AND NOT smSampleIsLadder AND (smPeakInCoreLadderLocus AND smSignalOL) AND smPartOfExtendedLocusRight
smAlleleHasExcessiveResidual = (smBPResidualTooLarge AND smSignalIsAllele) AND NOT smAmbiguousInterlocus

Triggers.TriggerExpression: smAmbiguousInterlocus (NOT (smRestrictedPriorityPeak OR smCalculatedPurePullup OR smExcessiveResidualDisplacement OR (smExcessiveResidualDisplacementLeft AND smExcessiveResidualDisplacementRight))): smAmbiguousExtendedLocusChannelPeaks
smPurePullupLateStage (NOT smRestrictedPriorityPeak AND NOT (smSampleIsNegCtrl OR smSignalIsCtrlPeak)): smNumberOfPullUpsInSample
smLocusContainsCrater (NOT smSampleIsLadder AND NOT smSampleIsNegCtrl): smLocusSummaryNumberOfCraters

Evaluations.Expression: smReportedHomozygoteHeightProblem = smHomozygoteHeightProblem AND (NOT smSampleIsPosCtrl OR NOT smDoNotReportHomozygoteHeightProblemForPositiveControlsPreset)
smNoYLinkedAlleleExpected = (smNoYForAMEL AND smSampleHasAMELLocus) AND smLocusIsYLinked
smLocusContainsPullUpWithHeteroImbalance = smHeterozygousImbalance AND smLocusAlleleHasPullup

smLocusUnderAmped = ((smLocusHasPeaksBetweenDetectionAndAnalysisThresholds AND (smNoGenotypeFound OR smReportedHomozygoteHeightProblem OR (smLocusHasPeaksBelowMinRFUThatAreNotKnownArtifacts AND smLocusIsHomozygous))) OR (smAmpMoreOnLowHomozygotePreset AND (smNoGenotypeFound OR smReportedHomozygoteHeightProblem))) AND NOT smSampleIsNegCtrl AND NOT smNoYLinkedAlleleExpected AND NOT (smLocusIsHomozygous AND smPeaksAboveHomozygoteValidityThreshold)

Triggers.TriggerExpression: smLocusIsHomozygous (NOT smSampleIsNegCtrl AND NOT smLocusIsYLinked): smTotalNumberOfHomozygousLoci
smNoGenotypeFound (NOT smSampleIsLadder AND NOT smSampleIsNegCtrl AND NOT smNoYLinkedAlleleExpected): smLocusDropout

Evaluations.Expression: smPossibleReampNegative = smLocusDropout AND smAlleleAboveOverloadLimit
smPossibleReampPositive = smLocusDropout AND NOT smAlleleAboveOverloadLimit
smPercentExcessiveResiduals = smNumberOfExcessiveResidualsInSample / smTotalNumberOfAllelePeaks
smPercentPullups = smNumberOfPullUpsInSample / smTotalNumberOfSignals
smIsSampleWithExcessivePullup = smNumberOfPullUpsInSample AND NOT smSampleIsLadder

smReampNegative = (smPossibleReampNegative OR (smIsSampleWithExcessivePullup AND smAlleleAboveOverloadLimit) OR smNumberOfCratersInSample OR (smSomePeaksHaveLaserOffScale AND smRecommendReworkIfLaserOffScalePreset)) AND NOT smSampleIsLadder
smReampPositive = (smPossibleReampPositive OR smAtLeastOneLocusUnderAmped) AND NOT smSampleIsLadder
smPossibleReampAmbiguous = smReampNegative AND smReampPositive
smSampleContainsTooManyExcessiveResiduals = smPercentExcessiveResiduals OR smNumberOfExcessiveResidualsInSample
smPossibleMixture = smLociWithMoreThanThreeAlleles OR smNoLociWithThreeOrMoreAlleles
smRecommendReampRegular = smNumberOfExcessiveResidualsInSample OR smPercentExcessiveResiduals OR smILSFailed
smRecommendReinject = smRecommendReampRegular
